reviewText: I loved BMFM as a kid and still love it now. If you haven't watched it I'd say give it a chance, maybe it wasn't as big as TMNT but is was just as good, these episodes were a couple of my favs and helped show how much the bros cared about each other.
I love this show from the 90's. Sad to see that they do not make a complete series DVD set.
I loved this show as a kid, sad to see that they do not make the season 1 DVD set anymore. Maybe in the near future. But for now I am buying the season 1 in VHS form.
I used to watch this cartoon when I was a small child. To bad that cartoons now adays are not like this anymore.
I used to watch this show as a young child. It does bring back good memories. Cartoons now adays are not like what they used to be.

I loved this show as a kid. It is reminecent of TMNT. I wish it was out on DVD in the States. They just don't make shows like this anymore.
